cycle", "url": "https://github.com/openhab/openhab-addons/pull/8038#discussion_r451716217", "createdAt": "2020-07-08T17:38:40Z", "author": {"login": "sprehn"}, "path": "bundles/org.openhab.binding.lgwebos/src/main/java/org/openhab/binding/lgwebos/internal/LGWebOSHandlerFactory.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -97,6 +97,7 @@ protected void deactivate(ComponentContext componentContext) {\n         super.deactivate(componentContext);\n         try {\n             this.webSocketClient.stop();\n+            this.webSocketClient.destroy();", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "62a1f151dcd15543208583f73e7a80f16b1cf78f"}, "originalPosition": 4}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "0bea83345548211751a99ba9fd46105a9dabcd4f", "author": {"user": {"login": "lolodomo", "name": "lolodomo"}}, "url": "https://github.com/openhab/openhab-addons/commit/0bea83345548211751a99ba9fd46105a9dabcd4f", "committedDate": "2020-07-10T06:43:39Z", "message": "Do not destroy the WebSocket client\n\nSigned-off-by: Laurent Garnier <lg.hc@free.fr>"}}]}}}, "rateLimit": {"limit": 5000, "remaining": 60, "cost": 1, "resetAt": "2021-10-28T19:08:13Z"}}}